data.title: Cupertino Union School District
data.text:
Cupertino Union School District is seeking input and ideas on the types of programs parents would like to have offered to students in Grades TK-8 during regular school hours.

A process completed in 2020, the Facilities Master Plan (FMP) has four main components: Cupertino USDâ€™s Educational Vision and Goals, the Facilities Condition Assessments, a Demographics Review, and a Financial Analysis.
